Edmond Ardisson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edmond_Ardisson 0 Edmond Ardisson (23 October 1904, in Marseille – 30 November 1983, in Jouarre) was a French actor. He appeared in more than ninety films between 1938 and 1983. Edmond_Ardisson ( 23_October_1904 , in Marseille – 30_November_1983 , in Jouarre ) was a_French_actor .
